E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('355','8','','1','0','0','0','','','','<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">瓷砖品牌如云，瓷砖电视背景墙品牌也不少。电视背景墙是近年提出的用于装饰客厅电视背景墙面的一个新的装饰概念，主要材料有瓷砖、玻璃、木质、软包等，瓷砖的特殊性、耐用性、装饰性使</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">瓷砖电视背<a name=\\\\\"_Hlt395616565\\\\\"></a></span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; font-size: 15pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><a name=\\\\\"_Hlt395616566\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\">景</span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">墙</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">运用最广泛。因此陶瓷行业电视背景墙瓷砖品牌如雨后春笋层出不穷，那么怎样才能突出重围？在众多</span></span><span><a href=\\\\\"http://www.hudsonhome.cn/xwzx/qyxw/2014-08-11/351.html\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">瓷砖</span><span class=\\\\\"15\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; color: rgb(0,0,255); text-decoration: underline; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">品牌</span></span></a></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">电视背景墙中脱颖而出呢？哈德逊瓷砖给您解答一下。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin-top: 0pt; text-indent: 21.75pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><strong><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 14px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: \\\\''宋体\\\\''; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">独一无二的砖属设计</s